don't give a shit.

1726
01:25:36,914 --> 01:25:39,785
Oh, my God. Dante. Dante.

1727
01:25:39,786 --> 01:25:41,265
Oh, my God,
those goddamn Romanos.

1728
01:25:41,266 --> 01:25:42,353
(ALDO EXCLAIMING)

1729
01:25:42,354 --> 01:25:43,746
