- Untie me.

1777
01:27:27,981 --> 01:27:29,982
Babe, this knot is impossible.

1778
01:27:29,983 --> 01:27:31,333
(GROANS) Hold on.

1779
01:27:32,072 --> 01:27:33,813
- (BITES)
- (SCREAMS)

