1790
01:27:52,963 --> 01:27:54,224
You're a big, fat, podgy baby.

1791
01:27:54,225 --> 01:27:55,530
You're a big, stupid,
blonde baby.

1792
01:27:55,531 --> 01:27:56,966
You're a baby with big poop
in your diaper.

