01:27:56,967 --> 01:27:59,011
- Mom!
- Don't move!

1794
01:27:59,012 --> 01:28:01,187
(GASPS) Oh, my God,
Bianca, you're alive!

1795
01:28:01,188 --> 01:28:03,015
Of course I am.

1796
01:28:03,016 --> 01:28:04,103
No, no, no...

1797
01:28:04,104 --> 01:28:05,715
Fabrizio is a terrible shot.

1798
