- (YELLS IN ITALIAN)
- (HOLLOW CLANGING)

1804
01:28:18,902 --> 01:28:21,251
- BIANCA: High tension steel.
- It's fucking cool, man.

1805
01:28:21,252 --> 01:28:22,514
(LAUGHS)

1806
01:28:23,428 --> 01:28:25,168
