so long. Sorry.

1808
01:28:27,171 --> 01:28:28,563
Oh, honey,
I'm just glad you're okay.

1809
01:28:28,564 --> 01:28:29,608
<i>Grazie, amore.</i>

1810
01:28:31,436 --> 01:28:32,741
