(TENSE MUSIC PLAYING)

1813
01:28:38,835 --> 01:28:40,793
(BULLETS WHIZZING)

1814
01:28:41,794 --> 01:28:43,186
(BIANCA CHUCKLES)

1815
01:28:43,187 --> 01:28:44,535
KRISTIN: Bianca,
take care of my kid, okay?

1816
01:28:44,536 --> 01:28:46,145
Make a break for the door.

1817
01:28:46,146 --> 01:28:48,409
I'll cover. Now!

1818
01:28:48,410 --> 01:28:49,627
