1819
01:28:49,628 --> 01:28:50,715
- Come on. Come on.
- (GUNSHOTS)

1820
01:28:50,716 --> 01:28:51,761
Go, go.

1821
01:28:52,892 --> 01:28:54,416
- Help me, Nicky.
- Come on.

1822
01:29:20,093 --> 01:29:21,834
